\*[SUP]42\*[SUPX]The queen of the south shall rise up in the judgment with this generation, and shall condemn it: for she came from the uttermost parts of the earth to hear the wisdom of Solomon; and, behold, a greater than Solomon is here.
\*[SUP]43\*[SUPX]When the unclean spirit  is gone out of a man, he walks through dry places, seeking rest, and finds none.
