\*[SUP]9\*[SUPX]And call no man your father upon the earth: for one is your Father, which is in heaven.
\*[SUP]10\*[SUPX]Neither be all of you called masters: for one is your Master, even Christ.
\*[SUP]11\*[SUPX]But he that is greatest among you shall be your servant.
