\*[SUP]14\*[SUPX]Afterward he appeared unto the eleven as they sat at food, and upbraided them with their unbelief and hardness of heart, because they believed not them which had seen him after he was risen.
\*[SUP]15\*[SUPX]And he said unto them, Go all of you into all the world, and preach the gospel to every creature.
