\*[SUP]15\*[SUPX]And as the people were in expectation, and all men mused in their hearts of John, whether he were the Christ, or not;
\*[SUP]16\*[SUPX]John answered, saying unto them all, I indeed baptize you with water; but one mightier than I comes, the latchet of whose shoes I am not worthy to unloose: he shall baptize you with the Holy Spirit  and with fire:
