\*[SUP]23\*[SUPX]And he said unto them, All of you will surely say unto me this proverb, Physician, heal yourself: whatsoever we have heard done in Capernaum, do also here in your country.
\*[SUP]24\*[SUPX]And he said, Verily I say unto you, No prophet is accepted in his own country.
