nd he looked up, and saw the rich men casting their gifts into the treasury.
\*[SUP]2\*[SUPX]And he saw also a certain poor widow casting in thither two mites.
\*[SUP]3\*[SUPX]And he said, Truthfully I say unto you, that this poor widow has cast in more than they all:
