\*[SUP]33\*[SUPX]And he said unto him, Lord, I am ready to go with you, both into prison, and to death.
\*[SUP]34\*[SUPX]And he said, I tell you, Peter, the cock shall not crow this day, before that you shall three times deny that you know me.
