\*[SUP]13\*[SUPX]And Pilate, when he had called together the chief priests and the rulers and the people,
\*[SUP]14\*[SUPX]Said unto them, All of you have brought this man unto me, as one that perverts the people: and, behold, I, having examined him before you, have found no fault in this man concerning those things whereof all of you accuse him:
