ow upon the first day of the week, very early in the morning, they came unto the tomb, bringing the spices which they had prepared, and certain others with them.
\*[SUP]2\*[SUPX]And they found the stone rolled away from the tomb.
\*[SUP]3\*[SUPX]And they entered in, and found not the body of the Lord Jesus.
