\*[SUP]23\*[SUPX]And Jesus answered them, saying, The hour has come, that the Son of man should be glorified.
\*[SUP]24\*[SUPX]Verily, verily, I say unto you, Except a corn of wheat fall into the ground and die, it abides alone: but if it die, it brings forth much fruit.
