\*[SUP]28\*[SUPX]Father, glorify your name. Then came there a voice from heaven, saying, I have both glorified it, and will glorify it again.
\*[SUP]29\*[SUPX]The people therefore, that stood by, and heard it, said that it thundered: others said, An angel spoke to him.
