\*[SUP]44\*[SUPX]Jesus cried and said, He that believes on me, believes not on me, but on him that sent me.
\*[SUP]45\*[SUPX]And he that sees me sees him that sent me.
\*[SUP]46\*[SUPX]I am come a light into the world, that whosoever believes on me should not abide in darkness.
\*[SUP]47\*[SUPX]And if any man hear my words,  and believe not, I judge him not: for I came not to judge the world, but to save the world.
\*[SUP]48\*[SUPX]He that rejects me, and receives not my words,  has one that judges him: the word  that I have spoken, the same shall judge him in the last day.
\*[SUP]49\*[SUPX]For I have not spoken of myself; but the Father which sent me, he gave me a commandment, what I should say, and what I should speak.
