\*[SUP]20\*[SUPX]For this cause therefore have I called for you, to see you, and to speak with you: because that for the hope of Israel I am bound with this chain.
\*[SUP]21\*[SUPX]And they said unto him, We neither received letters out of Judaea concerning you, neither any of the brethren that came showed or spoke any harm of you.
