\*[SUP]4\*[SUPX]For out of much affliction and anguish of heart I wrote unto you with many tears; not that all of you should be grieved, but that all of you might know the love  which I have more abundantly unto you.
\*[SUP]5\*[SUPX]But if any have caused grief, he has not grieved me, but in part: that I may not burden you all.
