or we know that if our earthly house of this tabernacle were dissolved, we have a building of God, an house not made with hands, eternal in the heavens.
\*[SUP]2\*[SUPX]For in this we groan, earnestly desiring to be clothed upon with our house which is from heaven:
\*[SUP]3\*[SUPX]If so be that being clothed we shall not be found naked.
