 therefore, the prisoner of the Lord, plead to you that all of you walk worthy of the vocation wherewith all of you are called,
\*[SUP]2\*[SUPX]With all lowliness and meekness, with longsuffering, forbearing one another in love;
\*[SUP]3\*[SUPX]Endeavouring to keep the unity of the Spirit  in the bond of peace.
\*[SUP]4\*[SUPX]There is one body, and one Spirit,  even as all of you are called in one hope of your calling;
\*[SUP]5\*[SUPX]One Lord, one faith, one baptism,
\*[SUP]6\*[SUPX]One God and Father of all, who is above all, and through all, and in you all.
