\*[SUP]13\*[SUPX]For every one that uses milk is unskillful in the word  of righteousness: for he is a babe.
\*[SUP]14\*[SUPX]But strong food belongs to them that are of full age, even those who by reason of use have their senses exercised to discern both good and evil.
