\*[SUP]3\*[SUPX]For this is the love  of God, that we keep his commandments: and his commandments are not grievous.
\*[SUP]4\*[SUPX]For whatsoever is born of God overcomes the world: and this is the victory that overcomes the world, even our faith.
\*[SUP]5\*[SUPX]Who is he that overcomes the world, but he that believes that Jesus is the Son of God?
