\*[SUP]19\*[SUPX]And we know that we are of God, and the whole world lies in wickedness.
\*[SUP]20\*[SUPX]And we know that the Son of God has come, and has given us an understanding, that we may know him that is true, and we are in him that is true, even in his Son Jesus Christ. This is the true God, and eternal life.
\*[SUP]21\*[SUPX]Little children, keep yourselves from idols. Amen.
