\*[SUP]26\*[SUPX]And he that overcomes, and keeps my works unto the end, to him will I give power over the nations:
\*[SUP]27\*[SUPX]And he shall rule them with a rod of iron; as the vessels of a potter shall they be broken to shivers: even as I received of my Father.
\*[SUP]28\*[SUPX]And I will give him the morning star.
